## Transaction Guidance

For Lynxtour, agentic shopping and catalog discovery should be treated as planning and inquiry support unless the user is booking a clearly fixed product and has explicitly confirmed the purchase path.

Agents must preserve the buyer-approval invariant for any checkout or payment action. For multi-day tours, bespoke custom itineraries, luxury private tours, private car charter, and any request with uncertain route or service details, require human Lynxtour specialist review before final booking or payment.
